king is boston and oxford educated and is held in high esteem throughout the country. guru rinpoche it is not possible to travel far in bhutan without seeing images of a man wearing a tall elaborate hat and with eyes that are open wide and staring forward into space. this is the great 8th century sage of vajrayana buddhism, padmasambhava or guru rinpoche as he often called. according to legend, padmasambhava was reincarnated into a lotus blossom as an eight year old child, and from very young he possessed great wisdom and insight. furthermore, he had mastery of the elements 